Additionally, while the Foundation\rquote s governing documents would not impose any additional fiduciary status upon the University, the decision to delegate to the University\rquote s Treasurer\rquote s office the responsibility of maintaining the Foundation\rquote s books and records, along with the responsibility of preparing a year-end settlement of the Foundation\rquote s expenditures effectively imposes an additional fiduciary status upon the University of that of a principal-agent relationship. 
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
