{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 is entitled, \u8220\'3fRelease or modification of restrictions on management, investment, or purpose\u8221\'3f. Moreover, UPMIFA, 
}
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=L&pubNum=1000005&cite=DESTT12S4706&originatingDoc=I91c5500bbf0311e1b66bbd5332e2d275&refType=SP&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.Default)#co_pp_a83b000018c76" }{\fldrslt 
